{"tid":1516566,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"做警察係原罪","createTime":"2019-08-29T15:12:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T02:20:21.000Z","uid":254742,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fce02fd59b94cbf8c720cb862d7a174bd2d1fbfb","tid":1516566,"uid":254742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:12:18.000Z","msg":"失業唔係罪，係不幸。搵唔到工唔係你嘅責任，要怪嘅，只好怪上帝。<br />\n<br />\n但係，做警察，就係你嘅錯！ 一個人好地地係唔會做警察嘅，你做得警察，梗係成日幻想行兇作惡啦。喺呢個有咁多工種嘅時代，你竟然做警察？警察係暴力嘅表現，係唔公義嘅象徵。警察囂張跋扈嘅氣焰，已經充分顯示出佢哋嘅唔道德。<br />\n<br />\n警察係罪犯，佢哋甚至比強姦犯、殺人犯更無恥。一般犯人都會掩飾自己犯咗嘅罪。但係警察，佢哋竟然係鏡頭面前濫用暴力，就好似一個強姦犯將犯案過程放上Youtube咁。你話，見到警察有乜辦法唔憤怒？<br />\n<br />\n所以，見到警察應該即刻鬧佢，就算唔鬧佢都要鄙視佢，我哋要透過侮辱嚟喚醒佢嘅良知。喺街見到警察唔鬧佢，就好似搭地鐵見到痴漢非禮學生妹唔出聲一樣。作為一個有良知嘅人，我哋應該出聲，應該鼓起勇氣挺身而出鬧到佢哋狗血淋頭！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa19d3a8562bf5d9e4eed02bb0d606b3e9a7a58","tid":1516566,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:20:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">【升級罷工全民自決】求置頂</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">聽日中午截止 Final call!!!</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1516317\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1516317</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jp9XfQH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjp9XfQH.jpg&h=b9f55540&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wOJ86Xo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwOJ86Xo.jpg&h=adb0bf0d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y3TJbo3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.c